---
import SectionStructure from '../../structures/SectionStructure.astro';
---

<SectionStructure idSection="testimonials" sectionClasses="bg-[#F2F2F2]" wrapperClasses="py-20 min-h-[250px] justify-center">
    <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-5 justify-center items-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center w-full pb-12 items-center relative md:w-1/2">
            <img src="/public/assets/testimonial/bg.png" class="absolute max-h-[400px] lg:max-h-[450px] -z-30" alt="" />
            <video autoplay loop muted controls src="/public/assets/testimonial/testimonial.mp4" class="w-[80%] object-contain rounded-[10px]"></video>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:w-1/2">
            <div class="bg-white shadow-lg flex rounded-[10px] md:px-10 md:py-16 pb-8 flex-col gap-3 p-3">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl">Dr. Mads Gilber</h3>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-lg font-medium">
                    Mads Gilbert is a Norwegian emergency medicine specialist who has made frequent trips to Palestinian refugee camps in Lebanon, the West Bank and Gaza since 1982.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-lg font-medium">
                    The Israeli government has permanently banned him from entering the Gaza Strip.“They forbid us to be there with them… but they can’t forbid us to help them!”
                </p>
                <span class="font-bold text-center md:text-lg lg:text-xl mt-3">He has donated more than <br class="xl:hidden" /> 200,000 kr.</span>
            </div>
            <p class="italic text-xl md:text-4xl">Don’t let hunger win. For many children, tomorrow could be too late.</p>
        </div>
    </article>
</SectionStructure>
